{"tid":1803492,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"金鐘「圍城」","createTime":"2019-12-30T08:38:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-30T10:57:06.000Z","uid":59618,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"0b22183630e4abbe6f1ca9c80efd52abcf18e56e","tid":1803492,"uid":59618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T08:38:58.000Z","msg":"【金鐘「圍城」】<br />\n<br />\n夏慤道中信橋至立法會一段行人天橋架起了圍網，由地面圍到橋頂，只有金鐘站出口至樂禮街一段不在網內。同時，由警總通往演藝學校的整段行人天橋亦架起了圍網，天橋上透過鐵網望向警總，防如置身籠牢。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/710476795704610/posts/2740432866042316/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F710476795704610%2Fposts%2F2740432866042316%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=LK0Ahc5Iz%2F4EhQQuEN3KkUtrSvVb5AcF94AlmVXjqEc%3D&h=b5c7671d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/710476795704610/posts/2740432866042316/?d=n</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果剪得爛既 呢到會唔會變相係最好既攻擊加防守位置<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"094199e95e82fa40ffe65834c39f2b267aea510c","tid":1803492,"uid":305536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T08:39:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>[極限挑戰] <span style=\"color: red;\">德國第三份聯署，最後48小時</span>，要多3萬人，連登仔做唔做到?<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1803447\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1803447</a><br />\n<br />\n德國減少對中國和其他非民主國家的依賴<br />\n<a href=\"https://epetitionen.bundestag.de/petitionen/_2019/_09/_01/Petition_98731.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fepetitionen.bundestag.de%2Fpetitionen%2F_2019%2F_09%2F_01%2FPetition_98731.html&d=LK0Ahc5Iz%2F4EhQQuEN3KkUtrSvVb5AcF94AlmVXjqEc%3D&h=8d3730b6\" target=\"_blank\">https://epetitionen.bundestag.de/petitionen/_2019/_09/_01/Petition_98731.html</a></blockquote>"},{"pid":"9b8cd3f4c3e2bf0724d06f9c4049132ac2b9a96a","tid":1803492,"uid":54014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T10:04:15.000Z","msg":"近幾次港島大遊